coalda
Class CoaldaVis

java.lang.Object
  coalda.CoaldaVis

public class CoaldaVis
extends java.lang.Object

Author:
kesslewd Usage: coaldaVis [ [evaluate | export ] Possible command line arguments: calculationID: loads the calculation with this ID on startup. evaluate: Evaluates the calculation with the ID in the first parameter and prints the result on the command line. Exits without starting the visualization. export: Exports the calculation with with the ID in the first parameter to the file is the third parameter. Exits without starting the visualization. Starting coaldaVis without any command line parameters will start the visualization with an empty screen. From there on you can use any of the above functions or calculate a new visualization.
